146
00:13:17,144 --> 00:13:20,304
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Shit! I won't let you!</i></b></font>

147
00:13:22,514 --> 00:13:23,984
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Even if I'm just half-way in front,</i></b></font>

148
00:13:23,984 --> 00:13:26,654
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>the road is still mine!</i></b></font>

149
00:13:26,654 --> 00:13:28,674
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I won't give you any space!</i></b></font>

150
00:13:31,854 --> 00:13:34,724
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I've got local pride, dammit!</i></b></font>

151
00:13:34,724 --> 00:13:36,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I won't let you pass!</i></b></font>

152
00:13:50,204 --> 00:13:52,844
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>What?!</i></b></font>

153
00:13:52,844 --> 00:13:56,414
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Idiot! There's not enough</i>
<i>room for you to get by!</i></b></font>

154
00:13:56,414 --> 00:13:59,244
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>There shouldn't even be any road there!</i></b></font>

155
00:13:59,244 --> 00:14:01,114
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>This is bullshit!</i></b></font>

156
00:14:01,114 --> 00:14:05,074
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>You... Where the hell are you driving?!</i></b></font>

157
00:14:08,754 --> 00:14:12,124
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I told you it would require
load shift techniques.</b></font>

158
00:14:12,124 --> 00:14:18,564
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Cornering at maximum speed places the
majority of load on the two outside tires.</b></font>

159
00:14:18,564 --> 00:14:24,074
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Accelerating at that point causes
increased load shift to the rear.</b></font>

160
00:14:24,074 --> 00:14:29,244
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>So both outer-side loads
are borne only by the rear?</b></font>

161
00:14:29,244 --> 00:14:33,954
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Correct. In other words, the driver
intentionally creates a strong load shift</b></font>

162
00:14:33,954 --> 00:14:37,384
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>and reduces as much load as
possible from the inner-side front.</b></font>

163
00:14:37,384 --> 00:14:39,444
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If you can do that...</b></font>

164
00:14:44,624 --> 00:14:49,894
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...then at full throttle, you can
shortcut directly above the ditch.</b></font>

165
00:14:53,404 --> 00:14:57,744
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>He passed me! Am... Am I dreaming?</i></b></font>

166
00:14:57,744 --> 00:15:01,234
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>What was that just now? What happened?!</i></b></font>

167
00:15:04,784 --> 00:15:07,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Try that again at the next right!</i></b></font>

168
00:15:07,514 --> 00:15:09,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>What the hell just happened?!</i></b></font>

169
00:15:09,514 --> 00:15:12,074
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Show me that again so I can see!</i></b></font>

170
00:15:22,134 --> 00:15:27,464
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Dammit! If an Eight-Six can do it, so can this!</i></b></font>

171
00:15:33,004 --> 00:15:35,614
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I don't feel my right front</i>
<i>tire gripping the ground!</i></b></font>

172
00:15:35,614 --> 00:15:37,774
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Is it in the air?</i></b></font>

173
00:15:41,654 --> 00:15:43,674
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I'm gonna fall!</i></b></font>

174
00:15:47,654 --> 00:15:49,994
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>It's no good! I can't get back up!</i></b></font>

175
00:16:29,434 --> 00:16:32,004
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--He wiped out!
--You okay?!</b></font>

176
00:16:32,004 --> 00:16:34,434
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This is bad...</b></font>

177
00:16:44,444 --> 00:16:46,344
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Are you all right?</b></font>

178
00:16:49,084 --> 00:16:50,884
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You're not hurt?</b></font>

179
00:17:06,774 --> 00:17:08,434
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>A crash at C-7?</b></font>

180
00:17:08,434 --> 00:17:09,804
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Was it Tohru?!</b></font>

181
00:17:09,804 --> 00:17:11,434
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Any injuries?</b></font>

182
00:17:13,374 --> 00:17:15,144
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I see.</b></font>

183
00:17:29,824 --> 00:17:34,734
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The Roadster was overtaken by the
Eight-Six and crashed. It can't race.</b></font>

184
00:17:34,734 --> 00:17:36,594
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You win.</b></font>

185
00:17:38,934 --> 00:17:40,904
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What's going on?</b></font>

186
00:17:40,904 --> 00:17:43,934
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What the heck is going on?!</b></font>

187
00:17:55,954 --> 00:17:59,854
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>At first glance I thought it was an R34 GT-R...</b></font>

188
00:17:59,854 --> 00:18:03,294
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I do like those FR GT turbos.</b></font>

189
00:18:03,294 --> 00:18:06,594
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's a nice hobby right there.</b></font>

190
00:18:06,594 --> 00:18:10,334
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Take a good look at the true</i>
<i>power of an ace driver.</i></b></font>

191
00:18:10,334 --> 00:18:12,024
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Fujiwara!</b></font>

192
00:18:19,104 --> 00:18:21,674
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm Atsuro Kawai.</b></font>

193
00:18:21,674 --> 00:18:23,774
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm Keisuke Takahashi.</b></font>

194
00:18:27,484 --> 00:18:30,984
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>He doesn't intimidate his</i>
<i>opponent, but at the same time</i></b></font>

195
00:18:30,984 --> 00:18:34,194
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>he doesn't seem to be</i>
<i>putting on any airs at all.</i></b></font>

196
00:18:34,194 --> 00:18:38,964
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>This is our home course, and he shouldn't</i>
<i>know anything about what I'm capable of...</i></b></font>

197
00:18:38,964 --> 00:18:41,484
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>So how can he be so calm?</i></b></font>

198
00:18:43,904 --> 00:18:45,964
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Just what is this?</i></b></font>

199
00:18:45,964 --> 00:18:48,804
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>This unknown feeling of intimidation?</i></b></font>

200
00:19:14,864 --> 00:19:16,164
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Atsuro...</b></font>

201
00:19:16,164 --> 00:19:20,004
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm shocked, Tohru. Even before we've started,</b></font>

202
00:19:20,004 --> 00:19:22,404
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I feel like I've been made
to walk to their rhythm.</b></font>

203
00:19:22,404 --> 00:19:25,604
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Don't think about it! Just keep your own pace.</b></font>

204
00:19:25,604 --> 00:19:28,574
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I couldn't, which is why that happened to me.</b></font>

205
00:19:28,574 --> 00:19:30,114
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah...</b></font>

206
00:19:30,114 --> 00:19:33,884
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Also, let me give you one piece of advice.</b></font>

207
00:19:33,884 --> 00:19:38,254
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>In the area starting around C-6, where
the drainage ditches are uncovered...</b></font>

208
00:19:38,254 --> 00:19:41,784
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Be sure not to open any room on the in-side,
and stay right on the corner line!</b></font>

209
00:19:43,124 --> 00:19:45,924
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If you open up more than a meter,
he's sure to go past you.</b></font>

210
00:19:45,924 --> 00:19:50,264
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>These bastards will shortcut
right over the ditch.</b></font>

211
00:19:50,264 --> 00:19:53,264
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What are you talkin' about, Tohru?
That's ridiculous.</b></font>

212
00:19:53,264 --> 00:19:56,574
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>These guys can do it!
Believe what I'm telling you!</b></font>

213
00:19:56,574 --> 00:19:58,734
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Do <i>not</i> open up any space on the in-side!</b></font>

214
00:20:00,974 --> 00:20:03,074
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Very well, let's begin.</b></font>

215
00:20:06,244 --> 00:20:09,614
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Don't let him pass you, Atsuro.
I'm counting on you!</b></font>

216
00:20:23,434 --> 00:20:29,574
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Atsuro... These are some</i>
<i>incredible drivers we're up against.</i></b></font>

217
00:20:29,574 --> 00:20:31,944
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>They let me know just how</i>
<i>big a gap there is between us.</i></b></font>

218
00:20:31,944 --> 00:20:36,904
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>You might not even have a chance of winning,</i>
<i>but at least make it through the first race!</i></b></font>

219
00:20:46,124 --> 00:20:50,624
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>These Project D guys are incredible!</i></b></font>

220
00:20:50,624 --> 00:20:52,964
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>It's like they have an aura!</i></b></font>

221
00:21:26,494 --> 00:21:28,124
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Welco--!</b></font>

222
00:21:30,664 --> 00:21:32,004
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hey there, Kenji.</b></font>

223
00:21:32,004 --> 00:21:34,504
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What the hell kind of face is that?</b></font>

224
00:21:34,504 --> 00:21:38,374
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Well, it's not like you're gonna
get any high-octane or anything...</b></font>

225
00:21:38,374 --> 00:21:44,084
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hey now! Anyway, I've got some news.
Project D has won again.</b></font>

226
00:21:44,084 --> 00:21:46,484
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Really?! Where this time?</b></font>

227
00:21:46,484 --> 00:21:47,814
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>In Tochigi.</b></font>

228
00:21:47,814 --> 00:21:49,584
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>How did Takumi do?</b></font>

229
00:21:49,584 --> 00:21:53,384
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He won, of course! And he
set a new course record.</b></font>

230
00:21:53,384 --> 00:21:57,424
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Looks like they won both
the uphill and downhill!</b></font>

231
00:21:57,424 --> 00:22:00,864
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Bit by bit, Takumi's moving up the ranks, huh?</b></font>

232
00:22:00,864 --> 00:22:03,264
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>As opposed to...</b></font>

233
00:22:03,264 --> 00:22:08,834
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Meaning we're no different from
ever, eh? Come on, don't say that.</b></font>

234
00:22:13,844 --> 00:22:16,774
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What? You're going to quit racing?</b></font>

235
00:22:16,774 --> 00:22:22,244
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That was the deal, wasn't it?
I lost last night's race.</b></font>

236
00:22:25,184 --> 00:22:29,794
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What's wrong, Tohru?! Did you hit
your head in yesterday's wreck?</b></font>

237
00:22:29,794 --> 00:22:31,424
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I don't like this. Get a hold of yourself!</b></font>

238
00:22:31,424 --> 00:22:33,364
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What are you talkin' about?</b></font>

239
00:22:33,364 --> 00:22:37,734
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You're the one who said
I had to quit racing if I lost!</b></font>

240
00:22:39,204 --> 00:22:44,974
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I know, but... I just said it trying to
be mean, because I was frustrated.</b></font>

241
00:22:47,144 --> 00:22:52,984
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's all right. It's actually a relief I lost. Really.</b></font>

242
00:22:52,984 --> 00:22:57,424
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Up till now, I thought that as a local,
I could never lose to any out-of-towner</b></font>

243
00:22:57,424 --> 00:23:02,554
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>and that I raced faster than anyone.
I had total confidence in myself.</b></font>

244
00:23:02,554 --> 00:23:09,064
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But I lost outright to some guy from another
pass, who'd only practiced for one night.</b></font>

245
00:23:09,064 --> 00:23:11,504
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Sure it was a shock,</b></font>

246
00:23:11,504 --> 00:23:15,804
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>but it feels good that when I got
beaten, it was done so perfectly.</b></font>

247
00:23:15,804 --> 00:23:17,604
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Tohru...</b></font>

248
00:23:19,474 --> 00:23:21,644
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Don't make that face, Naho.</b></font>

249
00:23:21,644 --> 00:23:25,344
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm not sayin' I'm never
gonna drive a car again.</b></font>

250
00:23:25,344 --> 00:23:29,414
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Simply toeing the line isn't
how a racer does things, right?</b></font>

251
00:23:29,414 --> 00:23:33,324
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm just gonna have a different relation
with cars than I have had up till now.</b></font>

252
00:23:35,094 --> 00:23:40,834
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It really was the best night.
I've never been that stoked.</b></font>

253
00:23:40,834 --> 00:23:44,664
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I think it was great that
I got to meet those guys.</b></font>

254
00:23:49,504 --> 00:23:55,774
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's like any profession... There are
very few who ever make it to the top.</b></font>

255
00:23:55,774 --> 00:24:00,884
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Those guys are probably among the select few.</b></font>

256
00:24:00,884 --> 00:24:04,484
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But I know now that I'm not.</b></font>

257
00:24:04,484 --> 00:24:08,684
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Project D... They really are awesome dudes.</b></font>

258
00:24:47,394 --> 00:24:53,404
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Project D? Oh, that team from Gunma
that people are talking about recently.</b></font>

259
00:24:53,404 --> 00:24:56,574
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>They're coming? Hm.</b></font>

260
00:24:56,574 --> 00:25:01,874
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What are you doing on the weekend, Tomo?
There are no races this week, right?</b></font>

261
00:25:01,874 --> 00:25:05,214
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>No races, but I'm busy with tests.</b></font>

262
00:25:05,214 --> 00:25:09,214
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hey, you're not trying to
drag me into this, are you?</b></font>

263
00:25:09,214 --> 00:25:10,754
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Of course not.</b></font>

264
00:25:10,754 --> 00:25:15,794
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>There's no need to worry.
I definitely won't lose.</b></font>

265
00:25:15,794 --> 00:25:18,424
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I swear it on the name of the Toudou School!</b></font>

266
00:25:46,754 --> 00:25:48,754
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Hey sanjou, new generation</i></b></font>

267
00:25:48,754 --> 00:25:51,664
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Atarashii jidai tourai o ima teishou</i></b></font>

268
00:25:51,664 --> 00:25:56,794
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Itsu made wasureta furi o shiteiru no?</i></b></font>

269
00:25:56,794 --> 00:26:01,904
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>(Chigiresou na heart no tension) Mune no uzuki</i></b></font>

270
00:26:01,904 --> 00:26:06,904
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Sono hitomi no oku, osaekirenai mono</i></b></font>

271
00:26:06,904 --> 00:26:12,344
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>(Sou matowaritsuku kono image) yoru o niramu</i></b></font>

272
00:26:12,344 --> 00:26:22,194
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Sou dare no kokoro ni te o</i>
<i>nobashite fureru subemo</i></b></font>

273
00:26:22,194 --> 00:26:27,124
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>shiranakatta futari, mou koko kara</i></b></font>

274
00:26:27,124 --> 00:26:32,264
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>(Hey sanjou new generation,</i>
<i>Hora, This will blast your love)</i></b></font>

275
00:26:32,264 --> 00:26:36,604
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Blast my desire, break off the barrier</i></b></font>

276
00:26:36,604 --> 00:26:42,314
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Nemutta yume o tatakiokoshite</i>
<i>(Kirisaku you na skill)</i></b></font>

277
00:26:42,314 --> 00:26:46,784
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Blast my desire, stronger than fire</i></b></font>

278
00:26:46,784 --> 00:26:53,684
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Jidai o furuwasete risky tune</i></b></font>

279
00:26:53,684 --> 00:26:57,024
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Blast my desire</i></b></font>

280
00:26:57,024 --> 00:27:01,294
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>(Atarashii jidai tourai o ima teishou,</i>
<i>be what you wanna be)</i></b></font>

281
00:27:01,294 --> 00:27:03,834
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Blast my desire</i></b></font>

282
00:27:03,834 --> 00:27:07,134
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Blast my desire, whoa whoa whoa yeah</i></b></font>

283
00:27:07,134 --> 00:27:12,704
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>(Atarashii jidai tourai o ima teishou,</i>
<i>break what you wanna break)</i></b></font>

